<style>
  .home-shell {
    display: grid;
    gap: 32px;
    animation: fadeIn var(--duration-slow) var(--ease-out) both;
  }

  .hero-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 32px;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #12101f 0%, #1a1530 50%, #0f1628 100%);
    color: var(--text);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 92, 252, 0.12);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -20%;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124, 92, 252, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-card h1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 52px);
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .hero-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    align-content: center;
  }

  .hero-stat {
    padding: 18px 20px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    transition: all var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .hero-stat:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-color: rgba(124, 92, 252, 0.2);
  }

  .hero-stat strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .hero-stat span {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .section-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: end;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .section-head h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .section-head p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .character-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .character-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    padding: 24px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transition: all var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-out);
    position: relative;
    animation: fadeIn var(--duration-slow) var(--ease-out) both;
  }

  .character-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
  .character-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
  .character-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
  .character-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .character-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
  .character-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }

  .character-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(124, 92, 252, 0.3);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md), 0 0 20px rgba(124, 92, 252, 0.15);
  }

  .character-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--accent-blue));
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .character-card h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .character-card p {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .character-card .meta {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .empty-card {
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .btn-brand {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c5cfc 0%, #9178ff 100%);
    border-color: rgba(124, 92, 252, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(124, 92, 252, 0.3);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    width: auto;
  }

  .btn-brand:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(124, 92, 252, 0.4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .hero-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="home-shell">
  <section class="hero-card">
    <div>
      <h1>把想说的话，交给一个真正有气质的角色来接住。</h1>
      <p>楼阁是一个安静的角色对话空间。你可以创建角色、写下他们的性格和状态设定，再慢慢把每段对话聊出自己的味道。</p>
      <p>不赶、不吵，也不故作花哨。只是给角色、故事和情绪留一个舒服的地方。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <strong>公开角色</strong>
        <span>在这里逛一逛，先挑一个顺眼的角色开始聊天。</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <strong>多用户空间</strong>
        <span>每个人都能拥有自己的角色、自己的会话和自己的节奏。</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stat">
        <strong>入口</strong>
        <span>aicafe.momentsofus.cn</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <h2>现在可以聊的角色</h2>
        <p>挑一个合眼缘的，看看会发生什么。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <% if (characters.length === 0) { %>
    <div class="empty-card">还没有公开角色。先注册一个账号，写下第一个角色吧。</div>
  <% } %>

  <% if (characters.length > 0) { %>
    <div class="character-grid">
      <% characters.forEach(character => { %>
        <div class="character-card">
          <div class="character-avatar"><%= character.name.charAt(0) %></div>
          <h3><%= character.name %></h3>
          <p><%= character.summary %></p>
          <div class="meta">由 <%= character.username %> 创建</div>
          <% if (currentUser) { %>
            <form method="POST" action="/conversations/start/<%= character.id %>" style="margin-top:16px;">
              <button class="btn-brand" type="submit">开始聊天</button>
            </form>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      <% }) %>
    </div>
  <% } %>
</div>
